frames.caption: A majestic figure is seated in an opulent setting, surrounded by a cascade of golden coins. The figure, adorned with intricate jewelry and a grand crown, holds a pot overflowing with wealth, exuding an aura of prosperity and divine presence.
frames.description: The scene depicts a divine or mythical figure in a richly decorated temple-like environment. The atmosphere is one of abundance and reverence, with golden coins and ornate decorations enhancing the sense of grandeur.

frames.caption: A majestic figure adorned with gold jewelry sits cross-legged amidst a cascade of golden coins. The figure, with a serene expression, holds a pot from which coins are spilling. The opulent setting is enhanced by intricate golden decor and warm, glowing light.
frames.description: The scene depicts a regal, divine figure in a richly decorated interior, surrounded by wealth and opulence. The atmosphere suggests a sense of abundance and prosperity, with the figure exuding calmness and authority.
